      "options": {
        "content": "## AI Observability — NeonCart\n\nStory-driven view. Tabs below jump to each section. Time picker (top-right) zooms in/out.\n\n**📑 Tabs (jump):** click a row title to expand · use *Dashboards → AI Observability* in the side nav for the lens deep-dives.\n\n**Stories on this page:**\n- 🚨 Tool & Specialist Errors — what's failing right now, who's responsible\n- 🏆 Gift Recommender — Model Winner — which model converts best (CTR · ATC · purchases · revenue)\n- 🎯 Gift Recommender — Quality Trend — helpfulness · groundedness · bias\n\n**Linked lens dashboards (collapsed rows below):** Tools · Cost · Latency · TTFT · Conversation · Sub-Agent · RAG · Errors · Evals · PII · Hallucination · Prompts · Business KPIs",
        "mode": "markdown"
      },
      "title": "",
      "type": "text"
