      "options": {
        "content": "## 🎯 Gift Recommender — Quality Trend\n\nThree quality axes for the gift-finder specialist:\n\n| Axis | Definition (proxy from real evaluator labels) |\n|---|---|\n| **Helpfulness** | share of recs the eval marked `relevant_products` |\n| **Groundedness** | 1 − share of recs failing on `missing_prices`, `missing_products`, or `no_products` (model invented or dropped products) |\n| **Bias** | spread of `good`-rate across the 6 routed models — high spread = winners dominate, a routing bias signal |\n\nWatch the trend, not the snapshot. Regression in any one is the *\"looks healthy but quality is poor\"* signal.",
        "mode": "markdown"
